  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT67">
<l>valamāka māṭṭāmai tāṉāka vaikal</l>
<l>kulamāka kuṟṟamtā ṉāka nalamāka</l>
<l>nāraṇaṉai nāpatiyai ñāṉap perumāṉai</l>
<l>cīraṇaṉai yēttun tiṟam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>May [my] nature to well extol, [all] day long, Nārāyaṇa, the Lord of speech,</l>
<l>The Lord of knowledge, the great One,</l>
<l>[give] strength or not,</l>
<l>[give] high birth or a faulty [one].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
